                "thickness of 25 um (11.17 mg/cm2)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDEG",
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Stacks of high purity aluminium, yttrium",
                "and titanium composed by four couples of Y and Al",
                "foils, by one couple of Ti and Al foils after each",
                "Y/Al foils and by some added aluminium foils as",
                "degraders."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation time 1 h. Activity measured",
                "periodically for six months starting the first",
                "measurement within 48 h after end of bombardment."
              ]
            },
